      sourceSituation: 'Books, lectures, correspondence, and archives survive; Popper’s later recollections of early disputes are influential but must be checked against contemporary records.', knownFor: ['Falsifiability', 'Conjectures and refutations', 'Critical rationalism', 'Problem of demarcation', 'Open society', 'Critique of historicism'],
